In human terms, a murder means life in prison, so why is it so very different in the case of animal cruelty? Is it possible to tighten up the laws regarding sentencing and punishment for people who commit these terrible acts against our furry (and feathery) friends? Help us! Join us! Share us! We animal lovers have the power - BE THE VOICE for these animals! If you agree that animals feel, suffer, love and the truth about their abuse should be exposed, please “like” our page. Thank you!  https://www.facebook.com/pages/Animal-Cruelty-Exposed/363725540304160 

